== 物理性質 ==
[[File:Solar_Storm_on_August_1,_2010.OGG|thumb]]日冕物質拋射的一系列影片。]]日冕物質拋射會從太阳表面，釋放出大量的物質到[[太阳风|太阳风]]和[[外层空间|外層空间]]。被釋放的物質是一種主要由电子和質子组成的[[等离子体|等離子體]]。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Howard |first1=T. A. |last2=DeForest |first2=C. E. |date=20 June 2012 |title=The Thomson Surface. I. Reality and Myth |url=https://www.boulder.swri.edu/~deforest/ewExternalFiles/The%20Astrophysical%20Journal%202012%20Howard.pdf |journal=The Astrophysical Journal |volume=752 |issue=2 |page=130 |bibcode=2012ApJ...752..130H |doi=10.1088/0004-637X/752/2/130 |access-date=9 December 2021 |archive-date=2022-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220323060644/https://www.boulder.swri.edu/~deforest/ewExternalFiles/The%20Astrophysical%20Journal%202012%20Howard.pdf }}</ref>

典型的日冕物質拋射有三種顯著特徵的任意一個或者全部特徵：低[[電荷密度|電子密度]]的空腔、緻密的核心（[[日珥|日珥]]，它會出現在日冕儀的影像中，顯示像是崁入在空腔中的明亮區域），以及一個明亮的前緣。在現有的觀察中，日冕物質抛射對磁場及太陽風影響都是以泡狀或者環狀呈現的。<ref name=":0" />

大多數的拋射發生在太陽表面的活躍區域，比如[[太陽黑子|太陽黑子]]群。這些區域的磁力線呈封閉，令其中的磁場強度足夠大，可以容納等離子體。這些磁力線打被打斷或削弱時，便會拋出物質，產生日冕物質拋射。然而，日冕物質拋射也可能發生在表面活動寧靜，但曾經很活躍的區域。在[[太陽極小期|太陽極小期]]的期間，日冕物質拋射主要形成於太陽赤道的日冕流帶；<ref>{{Cite web|title=Coronal Mass Ejection (CME) {{!}} Center for Science Education|url=https://scied.ucar.edu/learning-zone/sun-space-weather/coronal-mass-ejection|access-date=2022-05-23|work=ucar.edu|publisher=University Corporation for Atmospheric Research|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220526133822/https://scied.ucar.edu/learning-zone/sun-space-weather/coronal-mass-ejection}}</ref>在[[太陽極大期|太陽極大期]]，日冕物質拋射的來源是在緯度上分布較為平均的活躍區域。

以[[太陽和太陽圈探測器|SOHO衛星]]在1996年至2003年間的測量為基礎，日冕物質拋射的速度從{{convert|20|to|3200|km/s|abbr=on}}，平均速度是 {{convert|489|km/s|abbr=on}}。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Yashiro |first1=S. |last2=Gopalswamy |first2=N. |last3=Michalek |first3=G. |last4=Cyr |first4=O. C. St. |last5=Plunkett |first5=S. P. |last6=Rish |first6=N. B. |last7=Howard |first7=R. A. |date=July 2004 |title=A catalog of white light coronal mass ejections observed by the SOHO spacecraft |url=https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Nat-Gopalswamy/publication/260073213_A_catalog_of_white_light_coronal_mass_ejections_observed_by_the_SOHO_spacecraft/links/569722ea08aea2d74374ac73/A-catalog-of-white-light-coronal-mass-ejections-observed-by-the-SOHO-spacecraft.pdf |journal=Journal of Geophysical Research: Atmospheres |doi=10.1029/2003JA010282 |access-date=16 February 2022 |archive-date=2022-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220216154340/https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Nat-Gopalswamy/publication/260073213_A_catalog_of_white_light_coronal_mass_ejections_observed_by_the_SOHO_spacecraft/links/569722ea08aea2d74374ac73/A-catalog-of-white-light-coronal-mass-ejections-observed-by-the-SOHO-spacecraft.pdf }}</ref>約13小時至86天（極端值）內，拋射物質便能前進1天文單位的距離，平均時間是3.5天；拋出的質量平均為1.6×10<sup>12</sup> kg。但是因為日冕儀的測量只能提供平面的數極，因此對日冕物質拋射的質量估計值只是下限。拋射的頻率取決於[[太陽週期|太陽週期]]的階段：從接近[[太陽極小期|太陽極小期]]的大約每五天1次，到[[太陽極大期|太陽極大期]]附近的每天3.5次。 <ref>{{cite book |title=An Introduction to Modern Astrophysics |publisher=Addison-Wesley |location=San Francisco |first1=Bradley W. |last1=Carroll |first2=Dale A. |last2=Ostlie |page=390 |date=2007 |isbn=0-8053-0402-9}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=What is a Coronal Mass Ejection (CME)?|url=https://www.spaceweatherlive.com/en/help/what-is-a-coronal-mass-ejection-cme.html|access-date=2022-05-22|author=Space Weather Live|format=HTML|publisher=spaceweatherlive.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220316194128/https://www.spaceweatherlive.com/en/help/what-is-a-coronal-mass-ejection-cme.html}}</ref>因為日冕儀通常觀測不到來自太陽背面的日冕物質噴發，這個值也是下限。

在目前對日冕物質拋射的運動中，日冕物質有一個預加速階段，緩慢的離開[[光球|光球層]]；然後是快速地加速，遠離太陽；直到達到恆定的速度。但有例外，有些氣泡狀的日冕物質拋射，一直維持在最慢的速度，沒有明確的速度變化，而是在整個飛行過程中緩慢而持續的加速。即使有著明確加速階段的一些日冕物質拋射，預加速階段也常常不存在，或者未能觀測到。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Byrne |first=Jason P. |date=2010-09 |title=The Kinematics and Morphology of Solar Coronal Mass Ejections |url=https://arxiv.org/pdf/1202.4005.pdf |journal=arxiv.org |via=arxiv.org |access-date=2022-05-23 |archive-date=2022-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220523070212/https://arxiv.org/pdf/1202.4005.pdf }}</ref>

=== 行星際日冕物質拋射 ===
日冕物質拋射通常在1至5天內就會從太陽抵達地球。在傳播過程中，日冕物質拋射會與[[太陽風|太陽風]]和[[行星際磁場|行星際磁場]](interplanetary magnetic field,IMF)產生相互作用。行星際磁場會令慢速的日冕物質加速接近太陽風的速度；高速的拋射物質也會減速至接近太陽風的速度。<ref name="Manoharan2006">{{Cite journal |last=Manoharan |first=P. K. |date=2006-05 |title=Evolution of Coronal Mass Ejections in the Inner Heliosphere: A Study Using White-Light and Scintillation Images |url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/s11207-006-0100-y |journal=Solar Physics |language=en |volume=235 |issue=1-2 |pages=345–368 |bibcode=2006SoPh..235..345M |doi=10.1007/s11207-006-0100-y |issn=0038-0938}}</ref>在靠近太陽的地方具有最強的速度改變，但是即使在超過1天文單位外，甚至在[[火星|火星]]也可以測量拋射物質的速度改變；<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Freiherr von Forstner |first=Johan L. |last2=Guo |first2=Jingnan |last3=Wimmer‐Schweingruber |first3=Robert F. |last4=Hassler |first4=Donald M. |last5=Temmer |first5=Manuela |last6=Dumbović |first6=Mateja |last7=Jian |first7=Lan K. |last8=Appel |first8=Jan K. |last9=Čalogović |first9=Jaša |date=2018-01 |title=Using Forbush Decreases to Derive the Transit Time of ICMEs Propagating from 1 AU to Mars |url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/2017JA024700 |journal=Journal of Geophysical Research: Space Physics |language=en |volume=123 |issue=1 |pages=39–56 |arxiv=1712.07301 |bibcode=2018JGRA..123...39F |doi=10.1002/2017JA024700 |issn=2169-9380}}</ref>甚至超出[[尤利西斯号|尤利西斯號]]太空船的觀測，<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Richardson |first=I. G. |date=2014-10 |title=Identification of Interplanetary Coronal Mass Ejections at Ulysses Using Multiple Solar Wind Signatures |url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/s11207-014-0540-8 |journal=Solar Physics |language=en |volume=289 |issue=10 |pages=3843–3894 |bibcode=2014SoPh..289.3843R |doi=10.1007/s11207-014-0540-8 |issn=0038-0938}}</ref>日冕物質拋射的速度大約超過{{convert|500|km/s|abbr=on}}，會帶動[[终端激波|終端震波]]。<ref name="Wilkinson2012">{{cite book|title=New Eyes on the Sun: A Guide to Satellite Images and Amateur Observation|url=https://archive.org/details/neweyesonsunguid00wilk|publisher=Springer|first=John|last=Wilkinson|page=[https://archive.org/details/neweyesonsunguid00wilk/page/n110 98]|date=2012|isbn=978-3-642-22838-4}}</ref>當日冕物質拋射的速度，在與太陽風移動的[[参考系|參考系]]中的速度，超過當地的快速[[磁聲波|磁聲波]]時，就會發生這種狀況。使用日冕儀可以直接觀察到這種震波。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Vourlidas |first=A. |last2=Wu |first2=S. T. |last3=Wang |first3=A. H. |last4=Subramanian |first4=P. |last5=Howard |first5=R. A. |date=2003-12 |title=Direct Detection of a Coronal Mass Ejection–Associated Shock in Large Angle and Spectrometric Coronagraph Experiment White‐Light Images |url=https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1086/379098 |journal=[[天文物理期刊|The Astrophysical Journal]] |language=en |volume=598 |issue=2 |pages=1392–1402 |arxiv=astro-ph/0308367 |bibcode=2003ApJ...598.1392V |doi=10.1086/379098 |issn=0004-637X |access-date=2022-04-15 |archive-date=2022-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220415120651/https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1086/379098 }}</ref>在日冕，還會釋出第二型的無線電爆發(type II radio bursts)，它們被認為發生在2<sub>r s</sub>（[[太陽半徑|太陽半徑]]）以內，也與[[太陽高能粒子|太陽高能粒子]]的加速密切關連。<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Manchester IV |first=W. B. |last2=Gombosi |first2=T. I. |last3=De Zeeuw |first3=D. L. |last4=Sokolov |first4=I. V. |last5=Roussev |first5=I. I. |last6=Powell |first6=K. G. |last7=Kota |first7=J. |last8=Toth |first8=G. |last9=Zurbuchen |first9=T. H. |date=2005-04 |title=Coronal Mass Ejection Shock and Sheath Structures Relevant to Particle Acceleration |url=https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1086/427768 |journal=The Astrophysical Journal |language=en |volume=622 |issue=2 |pages=1225–1239 |bibcode=2005ApJ...622.1225M |doi=10.1086/427768 |issn=0004-637X |access-date=2022-04-15 |archive-date=2022-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220606225348/https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1086/427768 }}</ref>

=== 星冕物質拋射 ===
在其它恆星上觀察到少量的星冕物質拋射，{{as of|2016|lc=y}}發現的所有恆星都是[[紅矮星|紅矮星]]。<ref name="Korhonen2016">{{cite arxiv|title=Hunting for Stellar Coronal Mass Ejections|eprint=1612.06643|class=astro-ph.SR|first1=Heidi|last1=Korhonen|first2=Krisztian|last2=Vida|first3=Martin|last3=Leitzinger|first4=Petra|last4=Odert|first5=Orsolya Eszter|last5=Kovacs|display-authors=3|date=20 December 2016}}</ref>這些都是通過光譜學檢測到的，最常見的是通過研究[[巴耳末系|巴耳末線]]：由於[[都卜勒效應|都卜勒頻移]]，向觀測者而來的譜線在[[蓝移|藍移]]上導致不對稱的外形<ref name="Vida2016">{{Cite journal |last=Vida |first=K. |last2=Kriskovics |first2=L. |last3=Oláh |first3=K. |last4=Leitzinger |first4=M. |last5=Odert |first5=P. |last6=Kővári |first6=Zs. |last7=Korhonen |first7=H. |last8=Greimel |first8=R. |last9=Robb |first9=R. |date=2016-06 |title=Investigating magnetic activity in very stable stellar magnetic fields: Long-term photometric and spectroscopic study of the fully convective M4 dwarf V374 Pegasi ⋆ |url=http://www.aanda.org/10.1051/0004-6361/201527925 |journal=[[天文与天体物理学报|Astronomy & Astrophysics]] |volume=590 |pages=A11 |arxiv=1603.00867 |bibcode=2016A&A...590A..11V |doi=10.1051/0004-6361/201527925 |issn=0004-6361}}</ref>。這種吸收出現在恆星圓盤（比周圍物質的溫度低）時會被增強，當它輻射至圓盤外時，可以被觀測到。 星冕物質拋射的投影速度從≈{{convert|84|至|5800|km/s|mi/s|sigfig=2|abbr=on}}<ref name="Leitzinger2011">{{Cite journal |last=Leitzinger |first=M. |last2=Odert |first2=P. |last3=Ribas |first3=I. |last4=Hanslmeier |first4=A. |last5=Lammer |first5=H. |last6=Khodachenko |first6=M. L. |last7=Zaqarashvili |first7=T. V. |last8=Rucker |first8=H. O. |date=2011-12 |title=Search for indications of stellar mass ejections using FUV spectra |url=http://www.aanda.org/10.1051/0004-6361/201015985 |journal=Astronomy & Astrophysics |volume=536 |pages=A62 |bibcode=2011A&A...536A..62L |doi=10.1051/0004-6361/201015985 |issn=0004-6361}}</ref><ref name="Houdebine1990">>{{Cite journal |last=Houdebine |first=E. R. |last2=Foing |first2=B. H. |last3=Rodono |first3=M. |date=1990-11-01 |title=Dynamics of flares on late-type dMe stars. I. Flare mass ejections and stellar evolution. |url=https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1990A&A...238..249H |journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics |volume=238 |pages=249 |bibcode=1990A&A...238..249H |issn=0004-6361 |access-date=2022-06-28 |archive-date=2022-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220416085209/https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1990A%26A...238..249H }}</ref>。與太陽的活動來比較，其他恆星上的星冕物質拋射活動似乎並不是很普遍<ref name="Vida2016" /><ref name="Leitzinger2014">{{Cite journal |last=Leitzinger |first=M. |last2=Odert |first2=P. |last3=Greimel |first3=R. |last4=Korhonen |first4=H. |last5=Guenther |first5=E. W. |last6=Hanslmeier |first6=A. |last7=Lammer |first7=H. |last8=Khodachenko |first8=M. L. |date=2014-09-01 |title=A search for flares and mass ejections on young late-type stars in the open cluster Blanco-1★ |url=http://academic.oup.com/mnras/article/443/1/898/1486077/A-search-for-flares-and-mass-ejections-on-young |journal=Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society |language=en |volume=443 |issue=1 |pages=898–910 |arxiv=1406.2734 |bibcode=2014MNRAS.443..898L |doi=10.1093/mnras/stu1161 |issn=1365-2966 |access-date=2022-04-15 |archive-date=2022-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220307194220/http://academic.oup.com/mnras/article/443/1/898/1486077/A-search-for-flares-and-mass-ejections-on-young }}</ref>。

== 關聯太陽現象 ==
[[File:Close-up_on_launching_filament_(SDO-AIA,_304_Å).ogv|thumb]]正在發展階段的影片。]]

日冕物質拋射經常與其他的太陽活動現象同時發生，包括：
* [[閃焰|閃焰]]
* 爆發日珥(Eruptive prominences)
* X-射线的[[偏振|偏振]]<ref name="Tomczak2012">{{Cite journal |last=Tomczak |first=M. |last2=Chmielewska |first2=E. |date=2012-02-22 |title=A CATALOG OF SOLAR X-RAY PLASMA EJECTIONS OBSERVED BY THE SOFT X-RAY TELESCOPE ON BOARD YOHKOH |url=https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1088/0067-0049/199/1/10 |journal=The Astrophysical Journal Supplement Series |volume=199 |issue=1 |pages=10 |arxiv=1201.1040 |bibcode=2012ApJS..199...10T |doi=10.1088/0067-0049/199/1/10 |issn=0067-0049 |access-date=2022-04-15 |archive-date=2022-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220415120508/https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1088/0067-0049/199/1/10 }}</ref>
* 日冕昏暗（在太陽表面長時期的亮度衰減）
* [[莫爾頓波|莫爾頓波]]
* 日冕波動（來自噴發地點的明亮擴散前緣）
* 爆发後等离子体環（post-eruptive arcades）
日冕物質拋射與這些現象的很常同時發生，但是還沒有充分了解。例如，日冕物質拋射和閃焰經常是同時發生的。但發生日冕物質拋射時，經常未能檢測到太陽閃焰。大多數微弱的太陽閃焰和日冕物質拋射無關，只有強大的太陽閃焰（M級和更強的）才和日冕物質拋射相同時發生。有些較弱和較慢的日冕物質拋射發生時，則不會產生類似閃焰的現象<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Andrews |first=M.D. |date=2003-12 |title=A Search for CMEs Associated with Big Flares |url=http://link.springer.com/10.1023/B:SOLA.0000013039.69550.bf |journal=Solar Physics |language=en |volume=218 |issue=1/2 |pages=261–279 |bibcode=2003SoPh..218..261A |doi=10.1023/B:SOLA.0000013039.69550.bf |issn=0038-0938}}</ref>；現在認為。日冕物質拋射和太陽閃焰是由共同的原成因造成的（日冕物質拋射事件加速度的峰值，與閃焰輻射之峰值經常是一致的）。一般而言這些現象（包括日冕物質拋射）都被認為是[[太阳磁场|太陽磁場]]結構大規模變動所衍生的結果；是否造成日冕物質拋射，反映出[[太陽週期|太陽周期]]的[[星冕|日冕]]環境（即噴發可以被磁場結構所限制，或者它可以突破而成為[[太陽風|太陽風]]）。

對地球的衝擊[[File:Comparing_CMEs.ogg|thumb]]只有一部份日冕物質拋射會令擊中地球。如果地球被擊中，便會形成行星際日冕物質拋射（ICME），伴隨著日冕物質的[[激波|激波]]，會引發[[磁暴|磁暴]]，令地球的磁場被擾動，並可能進而破壞地[[地磁场|磁場]]。如果在日冕物質擊中日間一側，會令的磁場被壓縮；如果在日冕物質擊中晚間一側，則拖出[[磁层|磁尾]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Coronal Mass Ejection (CME)|url=https://scied.ucar.edu/learning-zone/sun-space-weather/coronal-mass-ejection|access-date=2022-05-23|work=scied.ucar.edu|publisher=Center for Science Education|archive-date=2022-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220526133822/https://scied.ucar.edu/learning-zone/sun-space-weather/coronal-mass-ejection}}</ref>當在夜晚側的磁層[[磁重联|磁重聯]]時，會在地球的[[大氣層|高層大氣層]]內釋放出[[功率|功率]]達到[[瓦特|兆瓦]]級規模的能量。其中一次最著名的事件是[[1989年3月磁暴|1989年3月磁暴]]，造成魁北克水力發電廠斷電。

拋射物質中的[[太陽高能粒子|太陽高能粒子]]可以地球[[天體的極#磁極|磁極]]周圍廣大的區域引起特別強烈的[[極光|極光]]。日冕物質拋射，與來自其它來源的[[耀斑|閃焰]]，可能會干擾[[無線電|無線電傳輸]]，並對[[人造衛星|人造衛星]]和[[電力系統|電力系統]]等設施造成損害，產生持久和大範圍的[[停電|停電]]的風險。<ref>{{Cite book|title=Severe Space Weather Events--Understanding Societal and Economic Impacts: A Workshop Report|url=http://www.nap.edu/catalog/12507|publisher=National Academies Press|date=2008-12-17|location=Washington, D.C.|isbn=978-0-309-12769-1|doi=10.17226/12507|quote=These assessments indicate that severe geomagnetic storms pose a risk for long-term outages to major portions of the North American grid. John Kappenman remarked that the analysis shows "not only the potential for large-scale blackouts but, more troubling, ... the potential for permanent damage that could lead to extraordinarily long restoration times."}}</ref><ref name="awst20130114">{{cite news|url=http://aviationweek.com/awin/major-solar-event-could-devastate-power-grid|title=Major Solar Event Could Devastate Power Grid|work=Aviation Week & Space Technology|first=Frank|last=Morring, Jr.|pages=49–50|date=14 January 2013|quote=But the most serious potential for damage rests with the transformers that maintain the proper voltage for efficient transmission of electricity through the grid.|accessdate=2018-12-11|archive-date=2018-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181018080739/http://aviationweek.com/awin/major-solar-event-could-devastate-power-grid|dead-url=no}}</ref>拋射物質中釋放的高能質子會導致[[電離層|電離層]]中的自由電子數量增加，特別是高緯度的極地。自由電子的增加，尤其是在電離層的D層，會增強對無線電波的吸收，引發極帽吸收（Polar Cap Absorption，PCA）事件，同樣干擾無線電通訊。

在高海拔地區、飛機上和太空站的人類，有可能暴露在相對更強烈的[[太陽質子事件|太陽質子事件]]，它可能由日冕物質拋射引發。太空人吸收的能量不會因為太空船的遮罩而減少，如果提供了任何的保護，則有可能導致吸收能量微量不均勻。<ref>[https://www.bbc.com/future/article/20131113-the-supernova-inside-your-plane 13th November 2013, bbc.com: Space radiation: Should frequent flyers worry?] Quote: "...Only very high-energy cosmic rays can reach our atmosphere at latitudes close to the equator...Cosmic radiation exposure levels during flights vary according to altitude, latitude and the space weather at the time...“Solar energetic particles events are difficult to assess, but being aloft at high latitudes during a big solar storm would be a large dose,” says Lockwood...", [https://web.archive.org/web/20210122095521/https://www.bbc.com/future/article/20131113-the-supernova-inside-your-plane backup]</ref><ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/3230807.stm 31 October, 2003, BBCNews: Solar storm surge 'not over yet'] Quote: "... Earlier this week, aircraft traversing the north Atlantic were confined to a narrow corridor to minimise radiation exposure, and astronauts on board the International Space Station (ISS) took shelter in its most shielded section. ...", [https://web.archive.org/web/20210913120748/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/3230807.stm backup]</ref>

=== 未來的風險 ===
根據預測科學公司的物理學家皮特·萊利（Pete Riley）在2012年發表的一份報告，在2012年至2022年這10年間，地球遭受等同於[[1859年太陽風暴|1859年太陽風暴]]水平的日冕物質拋射事件襲擊的機率是12%。<ref name="NASA-20140723a" /><ref name="Riley2012">{{Cite journal|title=On the probability of occurrence of extreme space weather events: PROBABILITY OF EXTREME EVENTS|url=http://doi.wiley.com/10.1029/2011SW000734|last=Riley|first=Pete|date=2012-02|journal=Space Weather|issue=2|doi=10.1029/2011SW000734|volume=10|pages=n/a–n/a|language=en|bibcode=2012SpWea..10.2012R}}</ref>

在2019年，研究人员使用[[韦伯分布|韋伯分布]]的方式，估计地球在未来十年被等同於[[1859年太陽風暴|1859年太陽風暴]]水平的日冕物質拋射事件的几率为0.46%至1.88%。<ref name="nasa201409212">{{cite web|title=CME Week: The Difference Between Flares and CMEs|url=http://www.nasa.gov/content/goddard/the-difference-between-flares-and-cmes|access-date=7 July 2016|date=21 September 2014|last=Gleber|first=Max|publisher=NASA|archive-date=2021-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314170612/https://www.nasa.gov/content/goddard/the-difference-between-flares-and-cmes/}}</ref>

